{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of chip"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSChip"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllChipComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ChipComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"chip","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") , spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and border  (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/4OUDS30AllChipComponentTokensProviderP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/4OUDS14TokensProviderP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent04ChipB6TokensP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeChipComponentTokensProviderC","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for chip component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomChipComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the chip component tokens you want.","","        override var chipSizeMinHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension500 }","","        override var chipBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthmediumt }","","        override var chipColorBgFocus: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorContentDefault }","","        override var chipSpaceInsetIconOnly: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineTall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomChipComponentTokensProvider: ChipComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(chip: CustomChipComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(chip: CustomChipComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let chipComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let chipComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.10.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/ChipComponentTokens-Im